reviewText: Kids love getting packages in the mail from Amazon, this movie for an Autistic girl who LOVES Home ALone, so obviously loved this one too !
This will forever be my favorite childhood movie. It never gets old.

this is a awesome movie. kevin is back and better than ever. the traps are funnier and so are marve and harry. this is a great sequel to a great movie. love the story, the comedy and the acting are all great. this is a classic just like the first one. great movie. if you have not seen this movie then I recommend you do
